title: Music Time Deluxe
description:
This is the music writer package that allows you to compose your own music and print it on clean professional sheets.

It will also play back your music sheets as MIDI, that's useful as a debugging tool. But getting the MIDI output to actually reproduce all you nuances ant traits is a lot of tedious work, so don't expect nice automatic pay, this is for producing music sheets and playing them with a real instrument

Windows 7 level. Comes complete with registration key

Note: the Windows installer will create fonts in your fonts database for the mudic notes, symbols, etc. You need to leave them installed, otherwise the software will start to silently output rubbish

Enjoy!
